.winattr
		Class:
		Property Template:
		Class DLL Name:
		Title: Stock Items Labels
		Accesories Enabled? No
		Visible? Yes
		Display Settings
			Display Style? Default
			Visible at Design time? No
			Type of Dialog: Modal
			Window Location and Size
				Left:   1.288"
				Top:    1.969"
				Width:  6.7"
				Width Editable? Yes
				Height: 1.604"
				Height Editable? Yes
